Package: hischooldata
Title: Fetch and Process Hawaii School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and processes school data from the Hawaii Department
    of Education (HIDOE). Provides functions for fetching enrollment data
    from official HIDOE sources and transforming it into tidy format for
    analysis. Hawaii is unique as the only U.S. state with a single
    statewide school district.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
